</div>


    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">
        <strong>29 July 1938</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 debate-date">Volume 338</div>

    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <div class="container">
            <div id="debateContent">
                <div class="highlightedSearchTerms"></div>
                <div class="content-container">


<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-273a2275-8fef-46e0-b16d-9c0287a0d791'>
            
<p class="">12.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-dc5671bb-eb60-4be5-9af8-84d14179a862">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-dc5671bb-eb60-4be5-9af8-84d14179a862">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-dc5671bb-eb60-4be5-9af8-84d14179a862">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-dc5671bb-eb60-4be5-9af8-84d14179a862">
                Mr. Tinker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dc5671bb-eb60-4be5-9af8-84d14179a862" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-07-29/debates/6721cece-8bff-4982-8885-8c4004a12403/Unemployment(ClosedMillsLancashire)#contribution-dc5671bb-eb60-4be5-9af8-84d14179a862">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the President of the Board of Trade whether his attention has been drawn to the closing down of a mill at Leigh that employed 300 people, and that two other mills employing 1,400 people have received notice that on 27th August they will close down for three weeks; and will he have inquiries made to find out the cause and to see whether anything can be done to ease the position?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-dc5671bb-eb60-4be5-9af8-84d14179a862" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-07-29/debates/6721cece-8bff-4982-8885-8c4004a12403/Unemployment(ClosedMillsLancashire)#contribution-dc5671bb-eb60-4be5-9af8-84d14179a862">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9 hs_ColumnNumber content-container " >
                <span data-toggle="tooltip" data-hop-debug-tooltip class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign hidden hidden-xs" data-placement="bottom" title=" hs_ColumnNumber "></span>

<p class="hs_ColumnNumber"><span id="3478" class="column-number column-only" data-column-number="3478"></span></p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-af5d500b-4a2e-4ad3-afcf-3cb5dd6a7994">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-af5d500b-4a2e-4ad3-afcf-3cb5dd6a7994">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-af5d500b-4a2e-4ad3-afcf-3cb5dd6a7994">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-af5d500b-4a2e-4ad3-afcf-3cb5dd6a7994">
                The President of the Board of Trade (Mr. Oliver Stanley)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-af5d500b-4a2e-4ad3-afcf-3cb5dd6a7994" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-07-29/debates/6721cece-8bff-4982-8885-8c4004a12403/Unemployment(ClosedMillsLancashire)#contribution-af5d500b-4a2e-4ad3-afcf-3cb5dd6a7994">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am informed that the first mill referred to has been closed on a transfer of its work to another part of Lancashire. I am also informed that the other two mills have been running full time for a number of years and that production has latterly exceeded demand. It is hoped to resume full time working after the interval of three weeks.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-af5d500b-4a2e-4ad3-afcf-3cb5dd6a7994" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-07-29/debates/6721cece-8bff-4982-8885-8c4004a12403/Unemployment(ClosedMillsLancashire)#contribution-af5d500b-4a2e-4ad3-afcf-3cb5dd6a7994">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-90faf315-0429-4371-be04-164238ba79b1">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-90faf315-0429-4371-be04-164238ba79b1">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-90faf315-0429-4371-be04-164238ba79b1">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-90faf315-0429-4371-be04-164238ba79b1">
                Mr. Tinker
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-90faf315-0429-4371-be04-164238ba79b1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-07-29/debates/6721cece-8bff-4982-8885-8c4004a12403/Unemployment(ClosedMillsLancashire)#contribution-90faf315-0429-4371-be04-164238ba79b1">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Can the right hon. Gentleman say whether anything is done by his Department to prevent this kind of happening, or to make preparations to absorb the unemployed when it does take place? After all, it is a serious matter for the people of Lancashire?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-90faf315-0429-4371-be04-164238ba79b1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-07-29/debates/6721cece-8bff-4982-8885-8c4004a12403/Unemployment(ClosedMillsLancashire)#contribution-90faf315-0429-4371-be04-164238ba79b1">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-24a3f74d-df78-4754-b75e-3d1e34e1a7f5">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-24a3f74d-df78-4754-b75e-3d1e34e1a7f5">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-24a3f74d-df78-4754-b75e-3d1e34e1a7f5">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-24a3f74d-df78-4754-b75e-3d1e34e1a7f5">
                Mr. Stanley
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-24a3f74d-df78-4754-b75e-3d1e34e1a7f5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-07-29/debates/6721cece-8bff-4982-8885-8c4004a12403/Unemployment(ClosedMillsLancashire)#contribution-24a3f74d-df78-4754-b75e-3d1e34e1a7f5">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Of course, there are two parts to this question. One is a mere temporary closing, and after the three weeks it is hoped that everybody will be absorbed again in the same undertaking. The other is part of a reorganisation scheme which will give a lot of work in another part of Lancashire, not very far away. Any question of transference, is a question for the Ministry of Labour.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-24a3f74d-df78-4754-b75e-3d1e34e1a7f5" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
